NAME:
	simulateP2Pcrypto

DESCRIPTION:
	A discrete-event simulator for a P2P cryptocurrency network

USAGE:
	simulateP2Pcrypto.py [-h] [--num_nodes NUM_NODES]
                            [--percent_slow PERCENT_SLOW] [--T_tx T_TX]
                            [--T_k T_K] [--start_coins START_COINS]

Simulate a P2P network

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  --num_nodes NUM_NODES
                        Number of nodes in the P2P network
  --percent_slow PERCENT_SLOW
                        Percentage of slow nodes in the network
  --T_tx T_TX           Mean of interarrival times of transactions on node
  --T_k T_K             Mean of random variable generated by node during PoW
  --start_coins START_COINS
                        Number of coins each peer has at the beginning
